{"tid":1066711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男包皮割到一半被漲價　醫生：感染念珠菌加價1萬人民幣","createTime":"2019-03-18T05:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T08:34:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f11a7c4f815918c774358c14429221745b37ab4c","tid":1066711,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:10:37.000Z","msg":"中國的醫院不時發生醫生趁病人接受手術時，臨時漲價、加收費用的事件，家住甘肅蘭州的孫姓男子成了最新的受害者。孫男周五（15日）向《梨視頻》投訴，稱他原本付了2000元人民幣（約9200.55元台幣）到蘭州愛德華醫院接受割包皮手術，沒想到躺上手術台後，醫生卻說，他的包皮被念珠菌感染，臨時加收費用，後來院方又在沒有事先說明的情況下，收取藥物費用，導致最後割包皮的費用高達1.2萬元人民幣（約5.52萬元台幣）。<br />\n孫男質疑醫院事前沒有清楚說明收費規則，等手術進行時才臨時喊漲，讓他「騎虎難下」。他又指控，醫院用他的身高、體重決定開藥份量及收費不合理。不過，執刀醫生反駁，他在術前已清楚說明收費內容，是手術時發現孫男的性器被念珠菌感染，才臨時加收消毒費用，孫男有同意。影片曝光後，當局已介入調查。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190318/640_ad2ee05117b5ef6e234455f7fda1ce2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190318%2F640_ad2ee05117b5ef6e234455f7fda1ce2f.jpg&h=cb96bda0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190318/640_a589cd73a1f5702b7b313d0a99c9d5a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190318%2F640_a589cd73a1f5702b7b313d0a99c9d5a7.jpg&h=ba278c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190318/1535115/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190318%2F1535115%2F&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=01e155ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190318%2F1535115%2F&h=2d0c2c44\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190318/1535115/</a>"},{"pid":"0754212ae41fa892ef40be9ce709b80486e1987d","tid":1066711,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-